{"tid":1240543,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我真係想知 乜道歉係咁既咩？","createTime":"2019-06-18T11:17:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T13:44:53.000Z","uid":20348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7120f60b0f3f0263ae7795cc65824d8491f0891d","tid":1240543,"uid":20348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:17:28.000Z","msg":"乜你有見過一個地方嘅領袖向民眾道歉會係用咁嘅方式咁嘅咀臉？<br />\n首先 <br />\n係數十分鐘記者會入面 <br />\n佢嘅說話 只不過係對件事上致歉 <br />\n我地由細到大被教同教人都係<br />\n對唔住 SORRY先係道歉 <br />\n你會唔會話: 我同你道歉。<br />\n咁就叫做左咩？<br />\n其次<br />\n地方領袖向民眾道歉<br />\n台都唔企出黎？<br />\n仲一副高高在上嘅咀臉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥 你咁算道歉？<br />\n<br />\n[size18] 我屌你老味啊 [/size18]<br />\n<br />\napp出 排版可能有問題 SORRY!"},{"pid":"c6f71fa9e5c89af481eaf3342a1ad926c09c869d","tid":1240543,"uid":20348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T13:21:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d0543b079192c417f9f9e53eb04f9b01d770662","tid":1240543,"uid":236878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T13:44:53.000Z","msg":"閪臉都算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />重點係完全無理訴求"}]}